window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Listen on if you dare! This unique in-world collection hallows the spooky tales and ghost stories that would have kept young Luke and Leia up at night. Created by George Mann and Grant Griffin—the same team behind the stunning Star Wars: Myths &amp; Fables—these seven frightful fables have been carefully woven from the expansive fabric that is the Star Wars galaxy.</p>"; 
